items.title: J.D.'s big week earns him NL honors
items.summary: J.D. Martinez's huge week at the plate has earned him the National League Player of the Week Award. The 30-year-old outfielder went 12-for-28 (.429) with seven home runs.
items.content: J.D. Martinez's huge week at the plate has earned him the National League Player of the Week Award. The 30-year-old outfielder went 12-for-28 (.429) with seven home runs.

items.title: Surging Hosmer earns AL honors for week
items.summary: Eric Hosmer is playing some of the best baseball of his life right now, and it's coming at the best time -- with his Royals fighting for a playoff spot and at the tail end of a contract year.
